12:06.000 --> 12:15.000
I believe that the most significant difference is that for the warehouse worker,

12:15.000 --> 12:29.000
the work is facilitated by the fact that the raw materials and their quality are discussed much earlier,

12:30.000 --> 12:39.000
both by the customer and the purchasing department, in order to ensure the incoming quality,

12:39.000 --> 12:50.000
while the warehouse worker of the finished product should pay great attention to the safety and completeness of the finished product.

12:51.000 --> 13:00.000
The decision on the type of transportation of the finished product and its cost is the competence of the loading managers.

13:00.000 --> 13:10.000
