13:10.000 --> 13:14.000
Let's talk in a nutshell about the storage process.

13:14.000 --> 13:28.000
The goal and the tasks of this function are storage, sorting and timely delivery of raw materials and finished products.

13:28.000 --> 13:33.000
Storage is an integral part of the delivery system.

13:34.000 --> 13:41.000
The main goals of the storage and storage process are reducing the costs of transportation,

13:41.000 --> 13:52.000
the possibility of product combination, improving the service level and the continuity of the production cycle.

13:52.000 --> 13:59.000
The main operations of the storage of raw materials and finished products can be illustrated as follows.

13:59.000 --> 14:06.000
The main tasks of the storage and storage process are receiving and checking the compliance,

14:06.000 --> 14:13.000
unpacking, re-packing, dividing into parts, combining and making the production mix,

14:13.000 --> 14:21.000
moving to the storage area, checking the quantity, writing off the defective raw material,

14:21.000 --> 14:26.000
and the final delivery of the finished product.

14:26.000 --> 14:34.000
The main tasks of the storage and storage process are the use of the storage area and the volume of the storage,

14:34.000 --> 14:41.000
the use of machines and mechanisms for moving the finished product,

14:41.000 --> 14:49.000
the creation and application of storage plans, the absence of so-called unoccupied islands in the area of the storage area,

14:49.000 --> 14:56.000
the availability of appropriate storage conditions, ventilation, access roads.

14:56.000 --> 15:04.000
In conclusion, I would like to note the importance and role of planning the management of the warehouse economy.

15:04.000 --> 15:09.000
When making a decision on the management strategy of the warehouse economy,

15:09.000 --> 15:16.000
it is necessary to take into account such factors as the form of ownership of the warehouse,

15:16.000 --> 15:24.000
the number of warehouses, the territory, the size, the availability of warehouse equipment.

15:24.000 --> 15:32.000
When talking about improving the operation of the warehouse, such criteria are usually taken into account.

15:32.000 --> 15:38.000
Reducing the distance between the loading and unloading points,

15:38.000 --> 15:44.000
increasing the number of raw materials or materials loaded into one movement,

15:44.000 --> 15:50.000
double-sided loading of warehouse equipment and the use of technologies.

15:50.000 --> 16:01.000
