20:30.000 --> 20:41.000
In this regard, the costs of transportation take up a significant place in the cost of the goods delivered to the enterprise.

20:41.000 --> 20:46.000
Along with other additional costs for loading and unloading,

20:46.000 --> 20:53.000
the price of the goods includes the cost set by the transport company.

20:53.000 --> 20:58.000
The price factor can include loading and unloading,

20:58.000 --> 21:02.000
packing requirements, special services,

